trans-unit.source: The BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator class is used internally by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_aspnet_regbrowsers" name="aspnet_regbrowsers" href=""></xref> tool to parse .browser browser definition files and add browsers to the run-time collection of known browsers contained in the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator er brukt internt av den <xref uid="langword_csharp_aspnet_regbrowsers" name="aspnet_regbrowsers" href=""> </xref> verktøyet til å analysere .browser leser filer, og Legg til nettlesere kjøretid-samlingen i kjente nettlesere som finnes i den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This class generates the source code for an assembly for the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory> class, which, at run time, produces request-specific <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase> objects to be publicly accessed through the ASP.NET intrinsic `Request.Browser` property.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen genererer kildekoden for en samling for den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory>klassen som produserer forespørsel-spesifikke ved kjøretid, <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase>objekter på offentlig tilgang via ASP.NET indre `Request.Browser` egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory>

trans-unit.source: Used internally to create a new instance of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Internt brukes til å opprette en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Used internally to coordinate the behavior of this class.
trans-unit.target: Brukt internt koordinere virkemåten til denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: This method first iterates through the "Browsers" folder.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden først går gjennom mappen "Nettlesere".

trans-unit.source: It then calls <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator.ProcessBrowserFiles%2A>, which loads and parses the XML contained in a collection of browser-definition files and inserts the information contained therein into an internal collection of browsers.
trans-unit.target: Kaller deretter <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator.ProcessBrowserFiles%2A>, som laster inn analyserer XML i en samling av nettleseren definisjon filer og setter inn informasjon der. i en intern samling med klientlesere.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesCodeGenerator.ProcessBrowserFiles%2A>

trans-unit.source: Then it calls an internal method which generates the source code compiles it, and registers it as an assembly in the global assembly cache for the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory> object.
trans-unit.target: Deretter kaller en intern metoden som genererer kilde kode kompilerer, og registrerer den som en samling i den globale samlingsbufferen bufre i den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory>objektet.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BrowserCapabilitiesFactory>

trans-unit.source: If necessary, this method then calls an internal method that restarts the Web server.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er nødvendig, kaller denne metoden deretter en intern metode som starter nettserveren.

trans-unit.source: Removes the browser capabilities factory from the global assembly cache and deletes its strong name public key token file.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner nettleseren funksjoner fabrikken fra den globale samlingsbufferen og sletter den sterkt navn offentlige token nøkkelfilen.

trans-unit.source: This method restarts the Web service.
The browser capabilities factory is then removed from the global assembly cache, and its strong name public key token file is deleted.
